title: Ep. 2839 - Good News And Garba - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 14 October 2019
shortDesc: Sundar calls Jethalal and tells him that he will bring Daya to Gokuldham society on Navratri. Jethalal is extremely happy and shares the good news with everyone. All of them are happy and eager to see Daya. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2840 - Sundar Arrives At Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 15 October 2019
shortDesc: Everyone does the puja for Navratri. They are all waiting for Daya to arrive. After a while, Sundar arrives at Gokuldham. He says that Daya has also come. Soon about five to six women come off the car. They have their faces hidden behind the veil.

title: Ep. 2841 - Test For Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 16 October 2019
shortDesc: Sundar brings on a test for Jethalal. He tells Jethalal to recognize Daya from among the nine women without removing their veils. Jethalal accepts the challenge and he tries. Jethalal plays Garba and unveils a few women but none are Daya.

title: Ep. 2842 - Daya Speaks To Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 17 October 2019
shortDesc: None of the women are Daya and Sundar tells everyone that Daya has gone for a Yatra and she couldn't come. However, Jethalal calms down and Daya makes it up over a video call. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2843 - Leakage In The Shop - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 18 October 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal meets Babita on his way to the shop. Jetha, Goli, and Babita speak about oranges. Jetha goes to the shop and gets a shock. He sees that there are leakages in the ceiling. He is worried and his employees make the issue even worse. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2844 - Jethalal's Troubles - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 21 October 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal has trouble coming his way. One after the other trouble and problems keep creeping up his way. He has a leakage, then he has a miscommunication with his plumber. He even finds his cash wet in the water. The leakage source is found.

title: Ep. 2845 - The Society Secretary - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 22 October 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal goes to the secretary of his shop's society. That person disturbs Jethalal and they return without a solution to the leakage. Jethalal gets an idea to call Bhide as he is the secretary of Gokuldham society, he may understand.

title: Ep. 2846 - A Rash Decision - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 23 October 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal doesn't get a proper solution to the leakage problem. Bhide, Popatlal, and Sodhi come to help him and they make a rash decision. They plan to enter the building to repair the leakage without permission and in an illegal manner. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2847 - The Gang Gets Caught - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 24 October 2019
shortDesc: All of the guys get into the house illegally and start fixing the leakage. They fix the leakage and everything is done when they get in trouble. Police come to the house and accuse them of being thieves. They all try to explain.

title: Ep. 2848 - Rough Jail Time - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 25 October 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal and the others are put into the jail. Jethalal tries to run away but he gets caught. The women are informed about this and they are worried. The policeman calls Chalu Pandey to ask about further proceedings.

title: Ep. 2849 - Misunderstanding Is Cleared - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 28 October 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal and the others meet Mr Iyer and his wife and explain what had happened. The owners of the house understand the issue and drop the charges on them. Chalu Pandey is also here and meets them. They get back home and face another trouble.

title: Ep. 2850 - Diwali Celebrations At Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 29 October 2019
shortDesc: All of Gokuldham society celebrate Diwali. They burst crackers and have fun at the festival of lights. Jethalal tries to take his father's blessings but one or the other person keeps coming. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2851 - Fun At Jethalal's Shop - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 30 October 2019
shortDesc: Nattu Kaka and Baga play a prank on Jethalal. Then they welcome him to the shop in a grand manner. After that, they have a couple of people who come to ask for their Diwali bonus. Customers start coming in and Jethalal has a great day.

title: Ep. 2852 - Back To The Same Old - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 31 October 2019
shortDesc: Everyone is back to their normal lifestyle after Diwali. Jethalal is lazy to wake up in the morning. Taarak is trying to avoid the bitter gourd juice made by Anjali but due to his bad luck, it keeps coming back to him. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2853 - Bhide's Troubles Don't End - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 1 November 2019
shortDesc: Bhide finds trouble early in the morning and then he faces a problem with the Auto Rickshaw driver. He also loses the keys to his home. Stay tuned.
